article_id:1143,category_name:News,title_name:A Gift of Items Useful for Unbinding the Mana Spiral!,image_path:,message:<div>We&#39;re giving all players 10 tempest orbs and 10,000 eldwater to help unbind the mana circles of adventurers who gained mana spirals at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1583991000"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This gift will be sent to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1584079200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>You can claim it from your goodie box for up to seven days after it&#39;s received. If the gift isn&#39;t retrieved within seven days, it will be lost.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1584079200,update_time1583738506